message.body: I'm going to be on campus today for a meeting 3:30-4:30. I'm eating dinner with melissa, but if you aren't overwhelmed, it would be nice to see you briefly! Sorry it's short notice, I'm terrible at communication.
Yes! Please :) what are you doing between 4:30 and dinner?
Also I might be in Philly next year! :)
We're eating an early dinner, so probably just going straight there. What are you doing now? I accidentally got here crazy early
